{"tid":1361901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我相信只有公務員全面罷工係最快救到香港既辨法","createTime":"2019-07-24T17:02:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T05:55:10.000Z","uid":226296,"like":134,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"29d85a1309ec5b97416d68899731a0846faef7c1","tid":1361901,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"其實政府部門同公營機構要開始拉隊遊行<br />\n<br />\n甚至罷工<br />\n<br />\n唔咁搞社會運動係唔會完<br />\n<br />\n而且新政府軍之後會仲恐怖<br />\n<br />\n尤其是有投資股票同樓既中高層公務員自己諗諗<br />\n<br />\n我當你地對7/21上環開36槍射頭事件視若無睹<br />\n<br />\n你地估7/21元朗恐怖襲擊只此一次?<br />\n<br />\n冇人會保障到香港人既身家性命財產<br />\n<br />\n而且你地當中應該有親戚住大西北<br />\n<br />\n你地都唔想佢地有事<br />\n<br />\n何況黑社會18區都有你地唔會知道下次喺邊發生<br />\n<br />\n只有令林鄭屈服<br />\n<br />\n接受五大訴求<br />\n<br />\n先可以令所有事件盡快平息<br />\n<br />\n各公務員公會要好好諗清楚"},{"pid":"ed04c805c4746f51d38eb1dade12fa9216f2f2bf","tid":1361901,"uid":3696,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"元朗手足有野講 727去唔去都入黎睇下<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1357311\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1357311</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8902110f956ce86d8837a3b0713b21b12cc84c61","tid":1361901,"uid":226296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:04:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0064ccdcedf1c49d611a522d8fb1fe260e34df78","tid":1361901,"uid":202889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"push 一齊罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f236935006dc32a3fb38cab65cafe404ba4147ef","tid":1361901,"uid":226296,"like"